{"title_page": "Mehazabien Chowdhury", "text_new": "{{BLP sources|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{short description|Bangladeshi actress}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Mehazabien Chowdhury\n| image              = \n| caption            = Chowdhury in 2016\n| birth_name         = Mehazabien Chowdhury\n| birth_date         = <!-- Please cite a reliable source for date of birth -->\n| birth_place        = \n| death_date         = \n| death_place        = \n| nationality        = [[Bangladeshi]]\n| occupation         = Actress\n| years_active       = 2009{{ndash}}present\n| net_worth          = <!-- Net worth should be supported with a citation from a reliable source -->\n| awards             = [[Lux Channel I Superstar]] (2009)\n| website            = [http://mehazabienofficial.com mehazabienofficial.com]\n| Birth date         = 19 April 1991 (age 28 years)\n}}\n'''Mehazabien Chowdhury''' is a Bangladeshi actress.  Chowdhury began her acting career after winning [[Lux Channel I Superstar|Lux Superstar]], a Bangladeshi beauty pageant in 2009, and rose to national prominence for acting ability.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://archive.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=123121 |title=Mehazabien Chowdhury crowned Lux Superstar \u201809 |last= |first= |date= |work=[[The Daily Star (Bangladesh)|The Daily Star]] |access-date=13 January 2015}}</ref>\n\nShe has acted in numerous TV dramas and came to limelight after acting in a TV commercial for mobile phone operator [[Banglalink]]. In 2017, she starred in a critically acclaimed television drama ''Boro Chele''.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/interview/mehzabien-didnt-realise-boro-chele-would-be-such-hit-1460707 |title=Mehazabien didn't realise \"Boro Chele\" would be such a hit |date=12 September 2017 |work=The Daily Star |access-date=23 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailystar.net/showbiz/grapevine/boro-chele-becomes-one-the-most-watched-bangladeshi-telefilms-youtube-1466134 |title=Boro Chele Becomes One of the Most Watched Bangladeshi Telefilms in YouTube |date=23 September 2017 |work=The Daily Star |access-date=23 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n==TV drama==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"|Year\n! scope=\"col\"|Drama\n! scope=\"col\"|Co-Artist\n! scope=\"col\"|Director\n! scope=\"col\"|Aired Channel\n! scope=\"col\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2009|| Tumi Thako Sindhupare || Mahmuz Ahmed|| Iftekhar Ahmed Fahmi||Channel I|| First TV drama\n|-\n| 2009\n| Odhora || Asif Azad\n| || ||\n|-\n| 2010\n| Chena Hoye Jai Ocehna ||Sajol || || ||\n|-\n| 2010\n| Unlimited Hasho || Ahona, Siddukur Rahman||Zia Uddin Alom ||RTV  ||\n|-\n|2010||Ring||Shohel Khan, Marjuk Rasel||Iftekhar Ahmed Fahmi||||\n|-\n|2012|| No Problem ||--|| ---||Bangla Vision|| Drama Series\n|-\n| 2013|| Opekkhar Photography || Afran Nisho||  Shikhor Shahoniat||NTV || Biggest Hit of the year \n|-\n|2013|| Moner Moto Mon ||Tahsan || Imraul Rafat||NTV ||\n|-\n|2013|| Tula Rashir Chele || Sajal|| || ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Oboshese Onnokichu || || || ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Tumi Rabindranather Omit Nou ||Sajal||Hasan Jahangir|| ||\n|-\n|2013|| Goru Jokhon Guru ||Sajal ||Rishita Jahan || Ekhushey TV||Telecast-ed on EID\n|-\n|2013|| Tiar Shes Porbo || Saju Khadem\n|Sanjay Barua ||Channel 9 ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Dhanda ||Mosharraf Karim, Mithila,Hasan Masud|| Shofikul Islam||Boishakhi Channel ||Drama Serial\n|-\n|2013|| Metro Politon Bivrom || || || ||\n|-\n|2013|| Tobuo Opekkhai || || || ||\n|-\n|2013|| Chokro || ||Anjan Aies || ||Drama Serial\n|-\n|2014|| Ekti Purbo Porikolpito Bibah ||Naeem||Sanjay Barua ||Masranga TV||\n|-\n|2014|| Vondo Jamai ||Sajal ||S. A. Haque Alik ||RTV ||Eid Ul Adha Special\n|-\n|2015|| Jamai Dhora ||Amin Khan ||Sanjay Barua ||Masranga TV||\n|-\n|2013|| Dorja Khola Chilo ||Sajal,Shahed,Romana,Bindu || Mohon Khan|| ATN Bangla||Telefilm\n|-\n|2013|| Vul Thikanai Jatra || Sajal,