s TV dramas and came to limelight after acting in a TV commercial for mobile phone operator [[Banglalink]]. In 2017, she starred in a critically acclaimed television drama ''Boro Chele''.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/interview/mehzabien-didnt-realise-boro-chele-would-be-such-hit-1460707 |title=Mehazabien didn't realise \"Boro Chele\" would be such a hit |date=12 September 2017 |work=The Daily Star |access-date=23 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thedailystar.net/showbiz/grapevine/boro-chele-becomes-one-the-most-watched-bangladeshi-telefilms-youtube-1466134 |title=Boro Chele Becomes One of the Most Watched Bangladeshi Telefilms in YouTube |date=23 September 2017 |work=The Daily Star |access-date=23 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n==TV drama==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"|Year\n! scope=\"col\"|Drama\n! scope=\"col\"|Co-Artist\n! scope=\"col\"|Director\n! scope=\"col\"|Aired Channel\n! scope=\"col\"|Notes\n|-\n| 2009|| Tumi Thako Sindhupare || Mahmuz Ahmed|| Iftekhar Ahmed Fahmi||Channel I|| First TV drama\n|-\n| 2009\n| Odhora || Asif Azad\n| || ||\n|-\n| 2010\n| Chena Hoye Jai Ocehna ||Sajol || || ||\n|-\n| 2010\n| Unlimited Hasho || Ahona, Siddukur Rahman||Zia Uddin Alom ||RTV  ||\n|-\n|2010||Ring||Shohel Khan, Marjuk Rasel||Iftekhar Ahmed Fahmi||||\n|-\n|2012|| No Problem ||--|| ---||Bangla Vision|| Drama Series\n|-\n| 2013|| Opekkhar Photography || Afran Nisho||  Shikhor Shahoniat||NTV || Biggest Hit of the year \n|-\n|2013|| Moner Moto Mon ||Tahsan || Imraul Rafat||NTV ||\n|-\n|2013|| Tula Rashir Chele || Sajal|| || ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Oboshese Onnokichu || || || ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Tumi Rabindranather Omit Nou ||Sajal||Hasan Jahangir|| ||\n|-\n|2013|| Goru Jokhon Guru ||Sajal ||Rishita Jahan || Ekhushey TV||Telecast-ed on EID\n|-\n|2013|| Tiar Shes Porbo || Saju Khadem\n|Sanjay Barua ||Channel 9 ||\n|-\n|2013\n| Dhanda ||Mosharraf Karim, Mithila,H