{"title_page": "Tanjin Tisha", "text_new": "{{short description|Bangladeshi actress, model and television presenter}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2019}}\n{{BLP sources|date=August 2017}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Tanjin Tisha\n| native_name        = \u09a4\u09be\u09a8\u099c\u09bf\u09a8 \u09a4\u09bf\u09b6\u09be\n| native_name_lang   = bn\n| image              = Tanjin Tisha dancing.jpg\n| caption            = Tisha in 2016\n| nationality        = Bangladeshi\n| occupation         = Actress, model, television presenter\n| years_active       = 2011\u2013present\n| awards             = [[#Awards and nominations|full list]]\n| Birth date         = 23 May 1991\n}}\n'''Tanjin Tisha''' is a Bangladeshi actress, model and television presenter. She has acted in television serials and dramas. She won [[Meril Prothom Alo Awards]] in ''Best Newcomer'' category for her performance in the drama ''U-turn''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/showbiz/tanjin-tisha-bangladeshi-popular-actress-1849138|title=Tanjin Tisha|date=2020-01-04|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-01-06}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nTisha started her career through fashion shoot and ramp modelling in 2011. Tisha first modeled in an advertising campaign of ''Robi'' directed by [[Amitabh Reza Chowdhury]] in 2012. That was the turning point of her career. <ref name=Showbiz>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbiznewsbd.com/2015/09/ekjon-shofol-tanjin-tishar-golpo.html|title=\u098f\u0995\u099c\u09a8 \u09b8\u09ab\u09b2 \u09a4\u09be\u09a8\u099c\u09bf\u09a8 \u09a4\u09bf\u09b6\u09be\u09b0 \u0997\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa|publisher=Showbiz News|first=Mahdi|last=Hasan|accessdate=28 September 2015}}</ref> She walked in ramp for ''Tresemme Fashion Show'' at [[Bangabandhu International Conference Centre]] on 18 September 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://photo.ntvbd.com/entertainment/bangladesh/tanjin-tisha/tanjin-tisha-dazzles-on-ramp/1442569142.ntv|title=\u09a4\u09bf\u09b6\u09be\u09b0 \u0986\u09b2\u09cb\u0995\u099a\u09cd\u099b\u099f\u09be|publisher=NTV Online|accessdate=28 September 2015}}</ref> She also acted in the music video of [[Imran Mahmudul]]'s ''Bolte Bolte Cholte Cholte'' which became popular on YouTube.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mzamin.com/mobile/details.php?mzamin=ODY2NDM%3D#.VcOYQnRoHLI.facebook|title=\u2018\u0987\u09ae\u09b0\u09be\u09a8 \u0986\u09ae\u09be\u09b0 \u09ac\u09c7\u09b8\u09cd\u099f \u09ab\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u09a8\u09cd\u09a1\u2019|newspaper=Manab Zamin|date=6 August 2015|accessdate=28 September 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nTisha learned dancing in her childhood but her family stopped it for her education. She completed her HSC from Siddhesshori Girls High School and College. Now, She wants to study film and media from a reputed university.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dhakarkhobor.com/2015/09/amader-showbiz-konna-tanjin-tishar-golpo.html|title=\u0986\u09ae\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b6\u09cb\u09ac\u09bf\u099c \u0995\u09a8\u09cd\u09af\u09be \u09a4\u09be\u09a8\u099c\u09bf\u09a8 \u09a4\u09bf\u09b6\u09be\u09b0 \u0997\u09b2\u09cd\u09aa|publisher=Dhakar Khobor|accessdate=28 September 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Drama!! Notes\n|-\n|2014||''[[U-Turn]]''||  won [[Meril Prothom Alo Awards]] in Best Newcomer category\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |\n| Apon Kotha ||  aired on NTV on Mothers' Day\n|-\n|Moyna Tia ||   drama serial aired on Asian TV\n|-\n|Sonali Roddur ||  \n|-\n|Kath Golaper Bosonto ||  \n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\"|2015||Palta Haowa||   drama serial aired on BanglaVision\n|-\n| Omimansito Sotto||   aired on BTV on Eid-ul-Adha\n|-\n| Megh Pakhi Eka||  aired on Bangla Vision on Eid-ul-Adha\n|-\n| Ei Sohore Meyera Eka || six episode serial aired on ATN Bangla on Eid-ul-Adha\n|-\n|Ochena Bondhu||  aired on ATN Bangla on Eid-ul-Adha\n|-\n|| Korban Alir Korbani||  appeared first time as a village girl and aired on Asian TV on Eid-ul-Adha<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.priyo.com/2015/Sep/21/17048